parts.text: I am doing well, thank you for asking! How are you today?
i am good. what are u?

I am a large language model, trained by Google. I don't have feelings or a physical body like humans do. I exist as a computer program that can process information and generate text. So, in a sense, I "am" a computer program.
Is there anything I can help you with?
Okay! Let me know if you think of anything. I'm here and ready to assist when you need me.
